    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/7b408d4b12cf67f1ef65024b4e1730f9.webp?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=51 /></span><br>▲ 合歡宗少宗主的異世界後宮冒險。<br>▲ 策略與休閑並重的Roguelike自走棋玩法。<br>▲ 性格、背景各異的異世界少女。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/e3749eb25908d468ad955432e080df3d.webp?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=51 /></span><br>一款帶有修仙元素的異世界穿越Roguelike遊戲。<br>你將扮演合歡宗少宗主開啟一段異世界後宮冒險。<br>為了讓宗門再次興盛，為了你心中的夢想、你的異世界後宮。<br>你是否會選擇毅然決然的踏入傳送陣前往未知的世界？<br>結實不同世界的同伴，面對未知的對手，你是否能化險為夷？<br>一起在路途中尋找答案吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/6e9e7dc17ea004d0b34663c92841901c.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/c1bb5f0b7eeecf8e66e80560fdf53989.webp?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=51 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/1159ff410f846c12323ce0ca494fb072.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >男主角</h2>修仙界合歡宗少宗主。<br>本應是天之驕子的少年不得不面對宗門已經衰落的現實。<br>踏入合歡宗後山的神秘傳送陣前往未知世界。<br>只為完成自己的夢想——<br>組建自己的異世界後宮。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/cb7b7753752167d0cf2e5541483cb231.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >青鳥</h2>陪伴在你身邊的侍女。<br>合歡宗實力排名前二的高手。<br>修仙界稱其為合歡宗的「嵐風鐵壁」。<br>與你一起經歷過不少磨難，<br>始終不離不棄。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/808d894520cca1681489e622df782618.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梵正鶯</h2>火炎焱春卷店的掌勺人。<br>春卷帽和披薩裙是她的標準穿搭。<br>有一批不怎麽忠誠但好吃的信徒追隨著她。<br>宗教裁判庭眼中的邪教頭子。<br>在與主角團相遇後她身上的另一個秘密將被揭示……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/ef16c83e2e6bb68598b579cb744e7247.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡莉娜</h2>在迷霧森林中遊蕩的銀發少女。<br>古靈精怪、性格囂張。<br>終日玩鬧，遊戲人生。<br>希望有一天能離開森林去往外界冒險。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/a1d14c1ee1e52c885051c11227b491c0.webp?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=51 /></span><br>帶有Roguelike元素的自動戰鬥玩法。<br>不同的搭配及同伴選擇帶來不同的戰鬥體驗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/246b1b793f0790617e4c600055c2bc5f.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>未知的敵人和強大的BOSS等待你的挑戰。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/68571c7066fc2811c804d13332fde37b.avif?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>與時空商人交易，擴充你的玩法組合。<br>數十張精美CG，直截了當的故事主題，從冒險故事到風花雪月，您想看到的場面會陸續呈現。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356360/extras/54c3011c9e503ca22dad0cf8182f2ad4.webp?t=1734500330\" width=500 height=51 /></span><br>▲ 《不雙修就去世》、《LOST：FIND》團隊最新作。<br>▲ 多個不同風格的世界。<br>▲ 策略與休閑並重的Roguelike自走棋玩法。<br>▲ 21位性格各異、不同種族的同伴。<br>▲ 超過20張精美的動畫CG。<br>▲ 幾十張趣味橫生的敘事CG。",
